@baseUrl = https://lacrei-saude-staging-395627369200.southamerica-east1.run.app/
@apiKey = 123

### Health check publico
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/

### Schema OpenAPI
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schema/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Swagger UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docs/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Auth: deve retornar 401 sem X-API-Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/

### Professionals: criar profissional
# @name createProfessional
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "social_name": "Dra Eline Silva",
  "profession": "Psicologia",
  "address": "Rua das Flores, 123 - Sao Paulo, SP",
  "contact": "eline@example.com"
}

### Professionals: listar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Professionals: filtrar por slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/?slug=dra-eline-silva
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Professionals: filtrar por profissao
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/?profession=Psicologia
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Professionals: detalhe usando ID criado acima
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/{{createProfessional.response.body.$.id}}/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Professionals: atualizar parcialmente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/{{createProfessional.response.body.$.id}}/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "contact": "eline.silva@example.com"
}

### Appointments: criar consulta para o profissional criado
# Cria/atualiza o paciente e sincroniza o cliente no Asaas.
# @name createAppointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "date": "2027-06-12T14:00:00-03:00",
  "professional": {{createProfessional.response.body.$.id}},
  "customer_name": "Pedro Algusto",
  "customer_document": "16071537002",
  "price": "300.00",
  "asaas_split": [
    {
      "walletId": "da80b358-2a5e-4969-8fa3-91ec4259a17d",
      "fixedValue": "300"
    }
  ]
}

### Appointments: listar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Appointments: filtrar por profissional
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/?professional={{createProfessional.response.body.$.id}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Appointments: filtrar por status de pagamento
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/?payment_status=PENDING
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Appointments: detalhe
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{createAppointment.response.body.$.id}}/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Appointments: listar consultas de um profissional
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/{{createProfessional.response.body.$.id}}/appointments/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Appointments: atualizar parcialmente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{createAppointment.response.body.$.id}}/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "customer_name": "Maria Oliveira Atualizada",
  "price": "350.00"
}

### Payment: consultar estado do pagamento
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{createAppointment.response.body.$.id}}/payment/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Payment: criar pagamento no Asaas
# Cria apenas a cobranca. O cliente Asaas ja foi criado na consulta.
# @name createPayment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{createAppointment.response.body.$.id}}/payment/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{}

### Webhook Asaas: evento processado quando existe asaas_payment_id correspondente
# Ajuste payment.id para um asaas_payment_id existente no banco.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/asaas/webhook/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "event": "PAYMENT_RECEIVED",
  "payment": {
    "id": "pay_123",
    "externalReference": "appointment:{{createAppointment.response.body.$.id}}"
  }
}

### Webhook Asaas: evento ignorado por referencia externa invalida
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/asaas/webhook/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "event": "PAYMENT_RECEIVED",
  "payment": {
    "id": "pay_123",
    "externalReference": "customer:123"
  }
}

### Validation: profissional invalido deve retornar 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "social_name": "   ",
  "profession": "Psicologia",
  "address": "Rua Um",
  "contact": "ana@example.com"
}

### Validation: consulta com data passada deve retornar 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "date": "2020-01-01T10:00:00-03:00",
  "professional": {{createProfessional.response.body.$.id}},
  "customer_name": "Joao Souza",
  "customer_document": "987.654.321-00",
  "price": "200.00",
  "asaas_split": [
    {
      "walletId": "wallet-percent",
      "percentualValue": "20"
    }
  ]
}

### Appointments: soft delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{createAppointment.response.body.$.id}}/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Professionals: soft delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/{{createProfessional.response.body.$.id}}/
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
